Merge pull request #13 from PiJoules/server_fixes

Be sure to move the type checks into the Validator constructor later and maybe isolate all the AssertionError messages into 1 message like "'route' must be an int. 'direction' must be one of ..."

Improve validation for /data

Did type conversion (e.g. string -> int) in try/except blocks, this way
we can check for None and bad integers at the same time and only need one
error message that works in both cases.

Handle exceptions in /data route

I moved the json response that we want into the try block so
any exceptions that are raised will get caught in the except clause

I also set the default for user_offset to 0 to essentially make it
optional.
